comment: Millsap (ATL) legally contests Johnson's (BKN) reverse layup attempt.
Lopez (BKN) makes "hi-five" contact with Horford (ATL) after the release which is legal.
Lopez (BKN) sets the screen on Teague (ATL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Jack (BKN) gets caught in the air and throws the ball before landing. He is the first player to touch the ball.
Jack (BKN) does not affect Teague's (ATL) RSBQ at the start of his drive to the basket.
Lopez (BKN) holds Teague (ATL) as he sets the screen without giving him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Korver (ATL) and Anderson (BKN) briefly engage during rebounding.
Lopez (BKN) makes incidental contact with Teague's (ATL) arm after the release that does not affect his shot attempt.
Anderson (BKN) cleanly knocks the inbounds pass away from Korver (ATL).
Jack (BKN) commits a take foul on Korver (ATL).
Jack (BKN) commits a take foul on Teague (ATL).
Carroll (ATL) does not affect Jack's (BKN) RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
Anderson (BKN) commits a take foul on Carroll (ATL).
